    </edge>
    <data key="d0">Sunday Sky's Personalized Video Rendering as a Service (RaaS)</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CgqEzyWpeA</data>
    <data key="d2">Sunday Sky provides personalized video experiences for their customers. This architecture describes their Rendering as a Service (RaaS) ecosystem, which generates personalized videos (e.g., Telco bills as video). WORKLOAD_PEEK: The system generates billions of videos yearly, millions daily. Key design decisions include cost-efficiency through spot instances, high availability via multi-AZ deployment and instance type diversification, and robust handling of spot interruptions and auto-scaling.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, interactive, compute_intensive, control</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
  </graph>
</graphml>
